Document: SkeletonModification2D
Path: godot/classes/class_skeletonmodification2d.rst
Summary: Base class for skeleton modifications in 2D.

SkeletonModification2D is the base class for all skeleton modification nodes in 2D. These nodes are used to modify the bones of a Skeleton2D at runtime. They are processed in the order they appear in the scene tree.

Inherits: Node2D < CanvasItem < Node < Object
